<br>
As has been pointed out several times in this thread, mob positioning is always important, and takes first presedence over most other considerations.<br>
<br>
Xuzl dps is pretty bland on PoP stuff, but any little bit helps.  Use it when you can and forget it exists when you can't.<br>
<br>
It is worth noting that you can dismiss Xuzl if you have your Familiar up.<br>
<br>
